      "description": "This is a vast office reimagined as a drained hot tub \u2014 the 'conference table' is a dry jacuzzi rimmed with clipboards. Three lifeguard chairs tower above, occupied by the interviewer trio radiating chaotic energy.",
      "image_url": null
    },
    {
      "id": "SANITARY_CELL",
      "name": "Test Sanitary Cell (Sector 7G)",
      "description": "A maze of pipes that seem to defy geometry line every wall. A neon-glowing toilet hums faintly as a boiler ticks like a mechanical heart ready to burst. The flickering fluorescent lighting adds a sense of impending, if absurd, danger.",
      "image_url": null
    }
  ],
